metadata.name: Incognito
metadata.description:
I prowl the night, to find various locations,
where people tread, in different situations.

A simple photo, is what I aim to achieve,
to be connected with people, no longer lonely.

Artists: DracheTech11 & Maurits (mjkvisuals)
